2. Real-time Trip Updates\
   - Current vehicle positions (where buses are right now)\
   - Predicted arrival times\
   - Delays and schedule adherence\
\
3. Service Alerts\
   - Service disruptions\
   - Detours, delays, closures\
   - Real-time notifications\
\
4. Stop Monitoring\
   - Real-time arrivals at specific stops\
   - Next bus info for any stop\
\
\
VISUALIZATION IDEAS\
