- Live Route Map - Show buses moving in real-time on a map\
- Stop Information - User searches a stop, sees next 5-10 arrivals\
- Service Status Dashboard - Current alerts and disruptions\
- Route Explorer - Browse all routes, see stops and schedules\
- Trip Planner Visualization - Show route options with timing\
- Analytics - Average delays by route/time, busiest stops, etc.\
